T04D3869:374b-1: tarka mungga ra k'a ri k'a n'a ma /
T04D3869:374b-3: rtog ge tho ba'i tshig le'ur byas pa zhes bya ba /
T04D3869:374b-4: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T04D3869:374b-5: yul dngos stobs kyis zhugs pa yi //
T04D3869:374b-6: tshad mas de nyid rtogs so zhes //
T04D3869:374b-7: chos kyi grags pa'i rjes 'brang ba'i //
T04D3869:374b-8: rtog ge ba rnams smra bar byed //
T04D3869:374b-9: blo gang bcad don thob byed pa //
T04D3869:374b-10: tshad ma yin zhes kha cig smra //
T04D3869:374b-11: la la ma rtogs don gsal 'dod //
T04D3869:374b-12: gzhan dag bden pa'i don rtogs smra //
T04D3869:374b-13: ha cang thal phyir ma 'brel ba //
T04D3869:374b-14: gzhan dang 'jal byed nyid ma yin //
T04D3869:374b-15: de phyir tshad ma'i gzhal bya ni /
T04D3869:374b-16: rdzas yod yin par smra bar byos //
T04D3869:374b-17: rdzas kyang skad cig ma nyid phyir //
T04D3869:374b-18: bcad don thob pa ga la srid //
T04D3869:374b-19: rgyun ltos shi na rgyun can las //
T04D3869:374b-20: gzhan med de min phyir rdzas min //
T04D3869:374b-21: bcad zhugs thob rgyun gsum phyir yang //
T04D3869:374b-22: rgyun ltos bcad don thob pa med //
T04D3869:374b-23: ldog pa gcig bcad rgyun ce na //
T04D3869:374b-24: rdzas ldog rdzas las gzhan min phyir //
T04D3869:374b-25: ldog pa gcig pa ga la yod //
T04D3869:374b-26: gal te rdzas gzhan ldog gcig na //
T04D3869:374b-27: gsal ba gzhan la spyi gcig la //
T04D3869:374b-28: ci yi phyir na khas mi len //
T04D3869:374b-29: gnyis ka rdzas yod 'gal zhe na //
T04D3869:374b-30: rdzas ldog rdzas las gzhan min pa //
T04D3869:374b-31: ci yi phyir na rdzas ma yin //
T04D3869:374b-32: gal te de nyid gzhan min na //
T04D3869:374b-33: smig rgyu la ni chu bzhin du //
T04D3869:374b-34: rdzas ldog rdzas su 'thad ma yin //
T04D3869:374b-35: de lta yin na tshad ma ni //
T04D3869:374b-36: dngos po'i yul can ma yin zhing //
T04D3869:374b-37: ma 'brel phyir na dngos med pa //
T04D3869:374b-38: tshad mas ji ltar 'jal bar byed //
T04D3869:375a-3: de phyir ldog pa gcig bcad kyi //
T04D3869:375a-4: rgyun ltos tshad ma mi 'thad do //
T04D3869:375a-5: rdzas rgyun yun rings mi gnas dang //
T04D3869:375a-7: ma rtogs don gyis gsal byed kyang //
T04D3869:375a-8: tshad ma'i mtshan nyid mi 'thad do //
T04D3869:375a-9: bden don rtogs pa tshad ma yi //
T04D3869:375a-10: mtshan nyid min te gang gi phyir //
T04D3869:375a-11: bden nyid grub pa med phyir dang //
T04D3869:375a-12: tshad min tshad mar 'gyur phyir ro //
T04D3869:375a-13: 'di ltar snang tsam bden snang dang //
T04D3869:375a-14: bden nges ldog pa gnyis ldan pas //
T04D3869:375a-15: yul bden yin par 'gyur zhig grang //
T04D3869:375a-16: log shes tshad mar 'gyur ba'i phyir //
T04D3869:375a-17: bstan ldog rnams kyis bden mi 'grub //
T04D3869:375a-18: ma bstan ldog pa gang zhig gis //
T04D3869:375a-19: bden pa 'grub pa'i thabs de smros //
T04D3869:375a-20: kha cig don du snang tsam gyis //
T04D3869:375a-21: bden mi 'grub kyang don byed par //
T04D3869:375a-22: snang bar bden pa nyid du 'dod //
T04D3869:375a-23: 'di mi rigs te gnyis kar yang //
T04D3869:375a-24: snang bar khyad par med phyir te //
T04D3869:375a-25: rtog bral 'jug yul mi ston phyir //
T04D3869:375a-26: mngon sum tshad ma nyid ma yin //
T04D3869:375a-27: khyab dang phyogs chos mi 'grub phyir //
T04D3869:375a-28: rjes su dpag pa yod ma yin //
T04D3869:375a-29: rang gi mtshan nyid yul can phyir //
T04D3869:375a-30: khyab pa mngon sum gyis mi 'grub /
T04D3869:375a-31: tshad ma yin phyir rjes dpag ni //
T04D3869:375a-32: yul dus spyi la 'jal mi byed //
T04D3869:375a-33: gang zhig spyi yi yul can min //
T04D3869:375a-34: de yi khyab pa ji ltar 'grub //
T04D3869:375a-35: shugs rtogs she na mi 'thad de //
T04D3869:375a-36: so sor nges pa'i yul can la //
T04D3869:375a-37: spyi la dmigs pa'i blo skye bas //
T04D3869:375a-38: de ni spyod pa yin par 'dod //
T04D3869:375a-39: ldog pa gcig dang tha dang dang //
T04D3869:375a-40: mtshungs pa gtan tshigs yin gyur grang //
T04D3869:375a-41: dang po med phyir phyogs chos med //
T04D3869:375a-42: gnyis gsum pa la khyab pa med //
T04D3869:375a-43: tshad ma med kyang khas blangs dang //
T04D3869:375a-44: 'gal phyir rang bzhin log rtogs sel //
T04D3869:375a-45: log rtogs log pa tsam zhig la //
T04D3869:375a-46: de nyid nges zhes tha snyad btags //
T04D3869:375a-47: rtog ge tho ba'i tshig le'ur byas pa nyi shu pa /
T04D3869:375a-48: kha che'i pandi ta dza ya a'a nan das mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T04D3869:375a-50: // / zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba khu mdo sde 'bar dang /
